dashboard.html
│
├─ Header (Logo + Mode Selector)
│   └─ Mode dropdown → HTMX → switch_mode_dynamic → updates session & fires JS event
│
├─ #mode-features  (dynamic zone)
│   └─ HTMX POST _mode_features → mode_features.html
│
├─ Journal Entry Card
│   └─ journal_form.html  (HTMX POST new_journal_entry)
│
├─ Mode Features / AI Insights Panel
│   └─ toggleAIInsights() swaps between:
│         → mode_features.html (cached)
│         → AI insights partial (from load_insight_panel)
│
└─ Sidebar
    ├─ Quick Actions (links to mode_explorer, search, etc.)
    ├─ Quick Stats
    └─ Daily Quote



mode_explorer.html
│
├─ Loops through modes
│   ├─ Activate Mode → set_selected_mode
│   └─ Set Preferred → set_preferred_mode
│
└─ Highlights active mode if matches active_mode



journal_form.html
│
├─ HTMX POST new_journal_entry
│   └─ On success:
│         → Reset form
│         → Refresh same_day_entries (entries.html)
│
entries.html
│   └─ Displays latest or same-day entries
│
check_entries.html
│   └─ Displays entries for specific date (filtered)
│
entryfilter.html
│   ├─ Date picker
│   └─ #filtered-entry-list → replaced by check_entries.html


synthesize_buttons.html
│
├─ Reflect   → hx-get synthesize_entries?type=reflect
├─ Digest    → hx-get synthesize_entries?type=digest
├─ Roast     → hx-get synthesize_entries?type=roast
└─ Suggest   → hx-get synthesize_entries?type=suggest

→ All results replace #synthesis-results with synthesis.html